snippet.title: Ainz Ooal Gown & Albedo Arrive in Esperia! | AFK Arena
snippet.description:
What is power? Is it the strength to crush your enemies, the control over vast territories, or the will to realize grand ambitions?

What if someone already has it all, but still craves more?

These beings know a thing or two about power. Behold: Ainz Ooal Gown - Magic Caster and Albedo - The Pure-White Devil!
